Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.v2x

Class V2xMessage

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.v2x.V2xMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Identifiable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cam, Denm, GenericV2xMessage, GreenWaveMsg, InterVehicleMsg, Ivim, Spatm, V2xMessage.Empty
public abstract class V2xMessage extends Object implements Serializable, Identifiable
Base class for any V2X message to be exchanged among simulation entities. Each V2xMessage requires to return an EncodedPayload object which holds the actual payload of this message (or just the length which might be sufficient for simulation). Furthermore, each V2xMessage requires a MessageRouting configuration which provides information about the communication path and addressing mode to use for simulating the transmission of this V2xMessage.
